      • invoke

        public static SWInvocationBean invoke(SWSessionBean ssn,
                                      java.lang.String verb,
                                      java.lang.String... args)
        Invoke. This is the primary entry point for the audio layer. A session object, plus the verb and direct objects are passed in. An invocation result object is passed back with all the text in it.
        Parameters:
        ssn - the session
        verb - the verb
        args - the direct objects for the verb
        Returns:
        the invocation context
